{"type": "article", "id": 3510, "title": "Nendo 两用布艺包袋", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-13T08:06:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232920vmwMtrAKPWRjgFa3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t收礼物时的心情总是很愉悦，可是一旦拆了礼物，美美的礼品包装就变成了废品。别急，日本设计团队 Nendo 带来了一个一举两得的解决方案,他们为自己旗下的文具品牌「 by | n」设计了一款名为「Giftote-bag」的两用布艺包袋，它带有一根包装礼品的彩带，扎起来时可以作为礼品的包装，而把它解开调整一下彩带的位置时，它会立马变身成为一个简单的托特包，提供 3 种不同的尺寸，并且可以调节包带长度。Giftote-bag 目前仅在日本西武百货发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232917qYD9Gs24khJILFZ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232918q8mKDh650kFl34dG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232918YIJwEMcNBOXimhU5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232918ubkyJrDPtTZL6CUg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232919VTZLoxgDjBMQS5qu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}